oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Proceedings of the Twenty-First Annual Conference (1988). Opening Ceremony
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Bovine Practitioners, American Association of
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The 21st Annual Meeting was launched in style with a Calgary Welcome Round-Up on Wednesday evening, September 28. It was a marvellous occasion to review old friendships and make new ones while enjoying an informal hot buffet, live western music, cash bar and Calgary hospitality.
